00:23:08.680 --> 00:23:08.971
" It was in the middle of the night—the trafficking and the things.

00:23:24.229 --> 00:23:27.093
And here we see Venezuela and all this stuff going on.

00:23:32.884 --> 00:23:33.062
Is this all coming about where you let your guard down?

00:23:33.062 --> 00:23:35.760
President Trump, be careful who you trust.

00:23:42.509 --> 00:23:42.880
Be careful who you let into your inner circle.

00:23:42.880 --> 00:23:58.150
Be careful who extends an olive branch of peace to you, saying, "Hey, we want to be your friend all of a sudden," when they were your worst enemy.

00:23:58.150 --> 00:24:02.080
Remember who is in your inner circle and who you're trusting.

00:24:02.080 --> 00:24:04.669
Do not trust so easily.

00:24:08.940 --> 00:24:10.200
Be watchful over who's in your inner circle and take no counsel from the ungodly.

00:24:10.200 --> 00:24:21.960
It's so important because all it takes is one bad decision to cause the house of cards to fall.

00:24:21.960 --> 00:24:24.095
China and Taiwan—all this major stuff.

00:24:24.095 --> 00:24:25.445
Let's pray and take communion.

00:24:25.445 --> 00:24:26.705
This is my favorite part.

00:24:26.705 --> 00:24:30.869
Every time I talk, I try to keep it as short as I can.

00:24:43.469 --> 00:24:43.851
So, Father, we just lift up this body before You.

00:24:43.851 --> 00:24:49.907
We're so thankful for this time of prayer and just seeking You, God.

00:24:49.907 --> 00:24:56.840
We're so thankful for where we are in these end times.

00:24:58.886 --> 00:25:07.190
I truly believe we're at that point like You said back in September—the point of no return where we're about to see an acceleration of things that's going to be shock and awe.

00:25:07.190 --> 00:25:08.040
Lord, I'm so grateful.

00:25:08.691 --> 00:25:11.640
I don't want to look at it and say life is bad.

00:25:11.640 --> 00:25:13.057
Lord, we're ready to get out of here.

00:25:16.926 --> 00:25:18.377
I'm just looking forward to being with You, not by death but by the rapture of the church.

00:25:18.377 --> 00:25:23.035
I'm so thankful, Father, that You are coming back and we'll be reunited with all our loved ones.

00:25:23.035 --> 00:25:24.520
It's just a glorious day.

00:25:24.520 --> 00:25:30.713
Oh, what a day of rejoicing that will be when we all get to heaven.

00:25:30.713 --> 00:25:32.075
We'll sing and shout the victory.

00:25:32.075 --> 00:25:33.320
Isn't that wonderful?

00:25:33.320 --> 00:25:35.343
It's going to be exciting.

00:25:35.343 --> 00:25:41.240
Everything we've ever believed for will be complete within our glorified bodies.

00:25:41.240 --> 00:25:46.616
We'll be standing before our King.

00:25:46.616 --> 00:25:50.394
Jesus Christ is coming; I just look forward to it.

00:25:56.329 --> 00:25:57.058
We take this body and thank You, Lord, for this time when everyone is focused on love.

00:25:57.058 --> 00:26:04.300
They say we focus on Cupid and all that stuff, but no, I just love my wife.

00:26:04.300 --> 00:26:10.980
We have an extra day of just loving each other—an extra day of being on a honeymoon.

00:26:10.980 --> 00:26:15.900
I think it's a good time to reflect and rekindle the fire in your marriage.

00:26:21.747 --> 00:26:21.980
You don't have to believe in all the weirdness.

00:26:29.960 --> 00:26:30.211
We just love each other, and it's a good day to love on your wife.

00:26:30.211 --> 00:26:37.166
Any day is a good day to love on your wife, but especially on Valentine's Day, try to be extra special.

00:26:38.005 --> 00:26:47.200
I think it's always good to sow love into the marriage and into the person who has given their life to you and given you children.

00:26:47.200 --> 00:26:49.810
Does that make sense?

00:26:50.605 --> 00:26:50.870
It's important.

00:26:50.870 --> 00:26:54.047
I think men don't need to be a fuddy-duddy.

00:26:57.484 --> 00:26:57.836
Be fun.

00:26:58.889 --> 00:26:59.240
Have fun.

00:26:59.445 --> 00:26:59.855
Be spontaneous.

00:27:02.255 --> 00:27:02.530
Love your spouse.

00:27:09.627 --> 00:27:09.760
Love your wives.

00:27:12.120 --> 00:27:12.520
Love your husbands.

00:27:12.520 --> 00:27:16.080
Pray with each other and honor each other.

00:27:29.983 --> 00:27:30.406
I really truly believe I can always feel when there's a flow in the spirit.

00:27:40.703 --> 00:27:41.011
I always say, "Okay, Diana, we've got to pray more together.

00:27:41.011 --> 00:27:43.420
We've got to read more together.

00:27:45.680 --> 00:27:47.440
" You can feel it when you're in a covenant relationship and you're pushing together.

00:27:47.440 --> 00:27:53.720
For where two or three are gathered together in my name, there I am in the midst of them—Matthew 18:20.

00:27:53.720 --> 00:27:54.400
All glory to God.

00:28:02.810 --> 00:28:03.060
I believe that's what happens when you pray with your spouse.

00:28:03.060 --> 00:28:07.560
If you say, "I don't have anybody," well, we'll be your two.

00:28:07.560 --> 00:28:09.360
Diana and I will agree with you.

00:28:09.360 --> 00:28:12.566
If you're single, we'll agree with you.

00:28:12.566 --> 00:28:16.293
That's why we're here—praying with you to agree with you.

00:28:16.293 --> 00:28:25.880
If you're a single mother or a single father and don't have anybody to agree with, Diana and I will agree with you.

00:28:29.280 --> 00:28:35.660
We pray and touch and agree, saying, "Whatever things are bound on earth are bound in heaven.

00:28:35.660 --> 00:28:42.164
Whatever things are loosed on earth are loosed in heaven.

00:28:43.738 --> 00:28:45.463
" We believe in the power of covenant and prayer.

00:28:45.463 --> 00:28:49.200
Whenever we agree, anything can be done.

00:28:49.200 --> 00:28:58.120
Two, three, four, or five agreeing—I believe with all my heart that many hands make light work.

00:28:58.120 --> 00:29:07.380
And so that's where we are in these end times—believing together as believers standing as a family.

00:29:07.380 --> 00:29:10.940
That's why we say "Good morning, family.

00:29:11.205 --> 00:29:14.890
" We believe it.

00:29:29.396 --> 00:29:29.671
We are the body of Christ.

00:29:29.671 --> 00:29:31.049
People say, "I'm Catholic.

00:29:32.825 --> 00:29:33.000
" I love the Catholics.

00:29:33.000 --> 00:29:35.114
Come on over here.

00:29:38.389 --> 00:29:38.691
We love the Church of Christ.

00:29:41.086 --> 00:29:41.383
We want the Baptists.

00:29:41.383 --> 00:29:45.720
We're not just about being charismatic here; we want the body of Christ.

00:29:45.720 --> 00:29:48.707
Now, you say, "Brandon, you say certain things.

00:29:48.707 --> 00:29:56.457
" Well, yes, because I believe certain things, but I'm just saying that out of love.

00:30:00.915 --> 00:30:01.180
We can agree to disagree.

00:30:01.180 --> 00:30:04.434
I don't always agree with my extended family.

00:30:07.942 --> 00:30:08.173
You don't have to agree with everybody.

00:30:08.173 --> 00:30:18.472
I have aunts that believe in the whole tribulation and things like that, and I agree to disagree, but I still love them.

00:30:18.472 --> 00:30:23.313
It's amazing when you can just love each other in spite of differences.

00:30:36.067 --> 00:30:36.253
We don't have to be mean.

00:30:38.360 --> 00:30:42.623
You don't have to be a "Sister Clipboard" and pick on people.

00:30:42.623 --> 00:30:45.229
Just say, "Hey, we love you.

00:30:46.811 --> 00:30:47.337
We don't have to agree on everything.

00:30:47.337 --> 00:30:48.600
You're entitled to your opinion.

00:30:51.293 --> 00:30:51.609
" We still love you.

00:30:51.609 --> 00:30:55.156
On this day, we can focus on love.

00:30:55.156 --> 00:31:01.080
Love takes no account of a suffered wrong as we get ready for the day of love.

00:31:01.080 --> 00:31:02.040
God is love.

00:31:02.040 --> 00:31:05.840
Walk in love in the days ahead because faith works by love.

00:31:05.840 --> 00:31:11.103
If you feel like your faith is stagnant, check your love walk.

00:31:11.103 --> 00:31:16.300
I don't always agree with what people say and preach from the pulpit.

00:31:16.300 --> 00:31:22.870
But as Brother Hagin used to say all the time, you have to eat the hay and spit out the sticks.

00:31:37.760 --> 00:31:37.920
There's something good you can find in anything, but you have to eat the hay and spit out the sticks.

00:31:39.744 --> 00:31:42.606
And so that's what we do.

00:31:42.606 --> 00:31:47.543
Find books that help you grow.

00:31:47.543 --> 00:31:51.497
So Father, we thank you.

00:31:57.220 --> 00:31:57.530
I thank you, Father, for the body, and we take it right now.

00:32:00.213 --> 00:32:08.405
We believe that we receive your healing power that flows on the inside of us in the name of Jesus.

00:32:19.040 --> 00:32:19.680
We take the blood.

00:32:20.320 --> 00:32:24.735
We apply the blood, and the blood makes much of us.

00:32:29.400 --> 00:32:30.840
We plead the blood over our homes and over our finances.

00:32:32.760 --> 00:32:39.800
We call those things that be not as though they were.

00:32:51.600 --> 00:32:52.100
We speak blessing, increase, multiplication, and favor over everything we put our hands to.

00:32:54.947 --> 00:32:59.983
We thank you, Lord, for what a God we serve, that we're blessed.

00:33:00.829 --> 00:33:04.470
We have increase, we have favor.

00:33:08.370 --> 00:33:26.790
We call in the financial seeds we sow; we call for a harvest over them: thirty, sixty, and a hundredfold.

00:33:55.400 --> 00:33:56.160
I speak to the seeds that I have sowed.

00:34:05.180 --> 00:34:06.785
You don't go dormant anymore; you spring forth much fruit in the name of Jesus.

00:34:06.785 --> 00:34:14.205
Now, angels of the Lord—we thank you, Lord—go, ministering spirits, and cause it to come forth in the name of Jesus.

00:34:20.899 --> 00:34:21.226
I call forth my harvest, a bountiful, beautiful harvest full of financial blessing.

00:34:21.226 --> 00:34:34.129
Now God, I thank you, Lord, that where I've sowed bad seed and we need a crop failure, I call for crop failure in the name of Jesus.

00:34:34.129 --> 00:34:36.653
I repent over the bad seeds I've sowed.

00:34:46.1000 --> 00:34:47.280
Thank you, Lord, they're washed in the blood.

00:34:47.280 --> 00:34:49.679
Father, we call for crop failure over those seeds.

00:34:49.679 --> 00:34:57.914
We thank you, Lord, that over the ones we sowed that were bad, we call for crop failure.

00:34:57.914 --> 00:35:02.440
We say your blessing and grace covers it in the name of Jesus.

00:35:10.613 --> 00:35:10.947
And we thank you, Lord, that your hand is on those good seeds.

00:35:10.947 --> 00:35:19.360
The bad seeds are drying up and going away; the birds are eating them because we don't want to reap bad stuff.

00:35:19.360 --> 00:35:21.580
Seedtime and harvest never cease.

00:35:21.580 --> 00:35:25.850
Whatsoever a man sows, that will he also eat.

00:35:29.000 --> 00:35:29.280
You have good seed and you have bad seed.

00:35:29.280 --> 00:35:30.760
That's what I'm talking about.

00:35:31.823 --> 00:35:33.880
You think, 'Well, everything is good in mine.

00:35:33.880 --> 00:35:34.660
' Baloney.

00:35:34.660 --> 00:35:39.930
There are times when you might have sowed some bad seeds.

00:35:40.950 --> 00:35:45.415
You might have treated somebody badly or spoken to someone badly.

00:35:57.260 --> 00:35:57.570
There are bad seeds.

00:36:05.156 --> 00:36:05.547
You might have done something wrong, treated somebody disrespectfully, or done them wrong in business.

00:36:13.698 --> 00:36:17.298
I don't want to reap that.

00:36:30.433 --> 00:36:30.907
Father, we ask for repentance over these things.

00:36:30.907 --> 00:36:33.889
I thank you, Lord, for the blood.

00:36:33.889 --> 00:36:41.832
That's why we plead the blood and we make much of the blood, and the blood makes much of us.

00:36:46.913 --> 00:36:48.467
We apply the blood of Jesus over us in the name of Jesus.

00:36:50.760 --> 00:36:51.150
And we thank you, Lord.

00:36:52.320 --> 00:36:56.360
We thank you for the weather, the rain, and the harvest.

00:36:57.377 --> 00:37:09.920
We thank you, Lord, for the grass growing, the trees, and all the birds and beautiful things that you're providing for us.

00:37:09.920 --> 00:37:16.980
It's almost springtime, and we're so grateful, Father, that the weather is turning even prettier right now.

00:37:17.590 --> 00:37:21.593
God, we give you praise and glory for it right now in Jesus' name.

00:37:21.593 --> 00:37:26.820
We take this blood and apply it over us in Jesus' name.

00:37:26.820 --> 00:37:28.180
Amen and amen.

00:37:28.180 --> 00:37:30.550
Lord, we thank you for it.

00:37:39.320 --> 00:37:39.570
Father, I thank you.

00:37:39.570 --> 00:37:44.760
Right now, I plead the blood of Jesus over anything you want to show us.

00:37:44.760 --> 00:37:55.091
So that it is uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic spirit, I apply the blood of Jesus over our prayer time.

00:38:09.280 --> 00:38:09.550
We thank you, Father, that the angels of the Lord are camping around and about us.

00:38:09.550 --> 00:38:17.515
Father, I plead the blood of Jesus over us, and we are not snared by any familiar spirits because we're always staying close to the Vine.

00:38:17.515 --> 00:38:18.720
Thank you, Father.

00:38:18.720 --> 00:38:23.030
We're so grateful for all that you've done and continue to do.

00:38:23.030 --> 00:38:25.937
We yield to the anointing of the prophet.

00:38:29.075 --> 00:38:29.230
I yield.

00:38:29.230 --> 00:38:33.844
Whatever you want to show me, Father, to warn the people, we humble ourselves before you.

00:38:33.844 --> 00:38:35.627
We attract to deflect.

00:38:35.627 --> 00:38:40.017
We don't use you; you use us.

00:38:40.017 --> 00:38:44.000
It's not about us trying to use you, Father.

00:38:44.000 --> 00:38:45.156
We're a vessel.

00:38:54.211 --> 00:38:54.520
You're the potter; we're the clay.

00:38:54.520 --> 00:38:55.960
We humble ourselves before you today.

00:38:55.960 --> 00:38:59.340
We know that apart from you, we can do nothing.

00:38:59.340 --> 00:39:01.825
As He is, so are we in this world.

00:39:17.680 --> 00:39:17.867
I thank you, Father.

00:39:17.867 --> 00:39:19.867
What can wash away my sin?

00:39:19.867 --> 00:39:22.630
Nothing but the blood of Jesus.

00:39:22.630 --> 00:39:25.053
What can make me whole again?

00:39:25.053 --> 00:39:27.240
Nothing but the blood of Jesus.

00:39:27.240 --> 00:39:31.623
Oh, precious is the flow that makes me white as snow.

00:39:31.623 --> 00:39:36.911
No other fount I know, nothing but the blood of Jesus.

00:39:36.911 --> 00:39:40.055
So Father, we just thank you, Lord, for this time.

00:39:44.916 --> 00:39:45.178
We plead the blood of Jesus Christ over every single one of us here.

00:39:45.743 --> 00:39:50.960
We thank you, Lord, that we're always in the right place at the right time.

00:39:50.960 --> 00:39:58.766
For the families up in British Columbia affected by the mass shooting, Father, I thank you that such things stop.

00:39:58.766 --> 00:40:03.290
We plead the blood over our children when they go into schools.

00:40:03.290 --> 00:40:05.253
No weapon formed against them will prosper.

00:40:07.217 --> 00:40:12.874
A thousand shall fall at their side and ten thousand at their right hand, but it will not come nigh.

00:40:12.874 --> 00:40:18.850
We take our authority over our school districts and over where our kids go to school.

00:40:18.850 --> 00:40:22.891
We plead the blood of Jesus over our children today.

00:40:22.891 --> 00:40:35.542
We thank you, Lord, that they will go into school and the light of God will shine on them so much that the teacher says, 'There's something different about your little girl, about your boy there.

00:40:35.542 --> 00:40:38.480
' And you say, 'Oh, it's because they have Jesus.

00:40:38.480 --> 00:40:44.340
' Because they're so used to heathens being around them, they go, 'There's something good about your kids.

00:40:44.340 --> 00:40:44.910
' Why?

00:40:44.910 --> 00:40:52.810
Because they stand out above everybody else, and the glory of the Lord is risen on your children.

00:40:52.810 --> 00:41:02.360
Arise and shine, for the light has come and the glory of the Lord has risen on our kids, our wives, and my husband.

00:41:02.360 --> 00:41:07.900
We believe that the angels of the Lord camp around and about them in the name of Jesus.

00:41:07.900 --> 00:41:11.555
Father, you go before us and you prepare the way.

00:41:11.555 --> 00:41:19.285
If you say, 'Don't go today, there's going to be something happening,' we're quick to hear you, Lord.

00:41:19.285 --> 00:41:22.754
We're quick to hear and obey.

00:41:22.754 --> 00:41:26.453
When you say, 'Don't go here,' we hear you.

00:41:33.470 --> 00:41:38.160
You told us in times past that there would be days ahead when if you don't listen closely concerning certain decisions you make for that day, there will be people who will not be there that night.

00:41:38.160 --> 00:41:43.813
They'll go home early because they're not following the voice of the Lord because of how dark these days are.

00:41:43.813 --> 00:41:57.840
If you have that inward check—for as many as are led by the Spirit of God are the sons and daughters of God—I believe that if you're led by the Spirit of God, He will lead you and guide you into all truth.

00:42:01.550 --> 00:42:01.775
You don't need a prophetic voice to tell you what to do.

00:42:01.775 --> 00:42:13.738
Right now, in the name of Jesus, we come before you, Father, boldly knowing that those who are led by the Spirit of God are the sons and daughters of God.

00:42:13.738 --> 00:42:18.354
We will be led by that peace that passes all understanding.

00:42:18.354 --> 00:42:21.213
You said, 'Follow that inward peace.

00:42:21.213 --> 00:42:24.227
Follow that peace that passes all understanding.

00:42:24.227 --> 00:42:28.792
' We will be led by the Spirit of God today.

00:42:28.792 --> 00:42:36.893
When you speak, we will hear your voice, and a stranger's voice we will not follow.

00:42:36.893 --> 00:42:49.184
We take authority over every demonic assignment, every plot, every plan, and every pursuit of wickedness concerning my life, our ministry, and the people on this channel.

00:42:49.184 --> 00:43:03.396
We believe, Father, that those who are led by the Spirit of God are the sons and the daughters of God, and they'll be led when it comes to where they're supposed to be living, working, and going to school or church.

00:43:03.396 --> 00:43:09.855
They'll be led by the Spirit of God.

00:43:10.645 --> 00:43:19.131
You say, "Hey, it's not just meant for you to be in whatever church you want to be at.

00:43:26.128 --> 00:43:26.624
" You should be led by the Spirit of God, for they are the daughters and the sons of God.

00:43:28.620 --> 00:43:39.315
Father, I believe that we're led by the Spirit today on where we're supposed to be at church, where we're supposed to be living, and where we're supposed to go to work.

00:43:39.315 --> 00:43:44.160
It's not what we think; it's because we're led by the Spirit of God.

00:43:47.960 --> 00:43:48.280
You say, "Well, I don't know about that.

00:43:48.280 --> 00:43:49.235
" I do.

00:43:51.440 --> 00:43:51.650
That's what the Word says.

00:43:53.653 --> 00:43:58.490
The Word says those that are led by the Spirit of God are the sons and the daughters of God.

00:43:58.490 --> 00:44:00.800
I believe that we're His children.

00:44:13.955 --> 00:44:14.180
We're His children and we will be led by His Spirit today concerning where we're supposed to live.

00:44:31.897 --> 00:44:32.194
You said, "Well, I don't want to live over there.

00:44:32.194 --> 00:44:34.858
" Well, the Lord said to live over there.

00:44:34.858 --> 00:44:36.084
I'm going to obey.

00:44:40.110 --> 00:44:40.460
I pray and obey.

00:44:40.460 --> 00:44:44.880
Well, He said, "I want you to move to Timbuktu.

00:44:44.880 --> 00:44:47.315
" Okay, Father.

00:44:47.315 --> 00:44:49.273
I'm on my way to Timbuktu.

00:44:54.373 --> 00:44:54.640
I don't know where that is, but I'm on my way.

00:44:54.640 --> 00:45:02.475
Well, I don't like it because they don't have this certain shop I like to shop at.

00:45:02.475 --> 00:45:07.912
Oh, I'm led by the Spirit of God because He has everything that is perfect.

00:45:07.912 --> 00:45:11.560
Every plan, everything that He has for you is perfect.

00:45:12.084 --> 00:45:15.845
And He knows your future more than you know your past.

00:45:15.845 --> 00:45:20.320
So, I will be led by the Spirit of God.

00:45:20.320 --> 00:45:26.489
You say, "Hey, I want you to work over here at this place.

00:45:26.489 --> 00:45:31.440
I'll give you favor over there and you'll be the manager.

00:45:31.440 --> 00:45:36.140
You're going to be the owner of that company before it's all over with.

00:45:36.140 --> 00:45:36.824
Go there.

00:45:36.824 --> 00:45:42.280
" Oh, Father, I'm led by Your Spirit.

00:45:46.060 --> 00:45:49.160
I don't know about that company, but I don't have to because I'm led by the Spirit of God.

00:45:49.160 --> 00:45:53.880
And the Spirit of God, peace that passes understanding, go with Your peace.

00:45:53.880 --> 00:45:59.600
If you have torment, fear has torment, but perfect love casteth out all fear.

00:46:09.433 --> 00:46:09.787
And that's why I say right now in the name of Jesus, they will be led by the Spirit of God today.

00:46:09.787 --> 00:46:14.089
They'll be led by the Spirit of God concerning where they're supposed to be.

00:46:14.089 --> 00:46:22.430
I'll be in the right place at the right time, doing everything the Lord has for me, every single day, every single waking moment.

00:46:22.430 --> 00:46:29.540
I will be where He calls me to be because I'm led by the Spirit of God.

00:46:46.240 --> 00:46:46.520
And I believe, Father, that they are led just like Diana and I are led.

00:46:56.823 --> 00:46:57.217
We pray together.

